info: This corpus is an automatically annotated version of data from the Parallel Bible Corpus (Mayer & Cysouw 2014) that has been reduced in scope for the purposes of crosslinguistic research. Metadata from the original PBC file is included in this dict for reference, as well as the license information and the automatic POS annotations. The first three characters of the filename corresponds to the ISO 639-3 code for the respective language. The `tagged` key in this dict contains a list of lists, with the first item in each sublist being the verse number (following PBC convention) and the second being a list of tuples in [word, POS] format where `unk` represents unknown tags.
license: This data is shared under a CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 license, and can be used solely for research purposes. The data is a selection of non-contiguous verses from a translation for the purpose of crosslinguistic research. Copyright of selected verses of each translation is retained by the original copyright holders.
metadata: #04013000 Jana Israel-warrangka bubu Sinai bawan , dungan , dungan , yubaku bubungu Canaan kadan . Yinya bubu Canaan Godungku jananda dajinka .
#09025000 Samuel wulan , Israel-warra wubulku murumarin , nyungunku badirin . Jana nyungun nandan nyunguwunbu bubungu Ramah .

#10014000 Davidamu kangkal Absalom , nyulu ngulkurrijin . Yamba nyulu bulmbuyman , kingmanka . Nyulu nyungu nganjan David karrnga-dajinka . Yinyaynka nyulu yiringkurrku dungan , bamanji ngulkurrku balkawan , yamba nyulu David binda-daman bamanda . Nyulu wawu jana nyungunku kurrkal-warrinka . Juma soldier-soldier wubul nyungunku kurrkal-warrin . Yinyamun nyulu and nyungu soldier-soldier kadan , Davidanji kuniwanka . Yamba Davidangka kuku nyajin , nyulu and nyungu soldier-soldier townmun Jerusalemmun warririn . Jana bubungu yuba wawubajanga Jordan balnji wunan , readyman , kuniwanka jananji Absalomanji . Absalomandamundu soldier-soldierangka David wukurrin , yamba Davidamu soldier-soldier jarra junkurrji , jananin beatim-bungan . Joab , nyulu maja Davidandamunku soldier-soldieranka . Nyulu Absalom yarkinkaku kunin . Yinyamun jana soldier-soldier and Israel-warra wubulku Davidandaku jurrkijin baja . Nyulu nyunguwunbuku bayanbaku dungan baja , bundan baja townbu Jerusalem .

#12025000 Nyubun king junkurrjiman bubungu Babylonia . Nyulu bubungu Judah kadan , Israel-warranji kuniwanka . Jana Israel-warra townbu Jerusalem murumarin . Yinyangkarr towndurr walls jirray gatesmunji . Jana Israel-warrangka gates wubulku nandan , soldier-soldier Babyloniamun kari walanka . Yamba Israel-warrangka God bayjanya , nyulu Babylonia-warra kari kirin jananin buyun-damanka . Juma jana Babylonia-warrangka walls dumbarrin , townbu Jerusalem walan , Israel-warra karrban , kanbal prisoner-bungan , bubungu Babylonia wundin . Nyulu kingangka soldier-warranda yalaman , “ Yurra , warru-warru dukul-ngulkurr wangkanyika Israel-warrandamun , bubungu Babylonia wundi . Ngayu jananin binal-bunganka , ngaykundu workmanijinka ngaykuwunbu bayanba jirraymba . ” Jana soldier-soldierangka warru-warru wangkanyin , nyubun burri Daniel . Godungku Daniel dukul-ngulkurr-bungan , mala-bijarr-bungan , Danielangka balkanka wanyurrinku bamangka junjuy bijarrin .

#18003000 Wawu yinyamun Job Godundu babajin , “ Maja God , ngayu wanyurrinku balkajin ? Wanyurrinku yundu Dubu kari kiril , bama warrngkay-maninka ? ” Yamba jana Jobundumundu jawunyungku nyungundu yalaman , “ Yundu malaji buyun-buyunku . Yinyaynka God kuli-kadan yununku , yinyaynka yunun buyun-daman . ” Jobungku yalaman , “ Kari . Ngayu kari buyun-daman . ” Jana Job nyuyan buyun-buyunku , yamba nyulu jananga kuku kari manin . Nyulu jananda yalaman , “ Yurra milka-janay , Godungku nganya buyun-daman , nganya babanka . Yurra manun-manunmaka ngaykunku . ”

#29001000 Godungku nyungu kuku prophetanda Joelanda dajin , bamanda Israel-warranda bubungu Judah balkanka . Nyulu yalaman , “ Yinja-yinja wubul bajaku kaday bubungu Judah . Jana mayi wubulku paddockmunbu nukal ; mayi corn , wheat yamba-kari , bamangka nukanka . Jikan yamba-kari , bulkingka , sheepangka , nanny goatungku nukanka , yinja-yinjangka wubulku nukanya . Yurra binga-bingangka yala kari nyajin jakalbaku . Godungku yinja-yinja kari kiril . Nyulu Israel-warra punishim-bunganka , jana nyungundumun jurrkijinya . Godungku balkal , ‘ Milka-bujarmaka yurrawunku buyun-buyunku ; jurrkijika baja ngaykunduku . Ngayu manun-manunmal yurranka , juma yurranda kaday . Juma ngayu ngayku wawu dajil bamanda wubulimbaku . Yinyamun jana warru-warrungku , and maral-maralangka ngayku kuku yirrkay yiringkurrku . Jana binga-bingangka bijarr bijarril , ngayu nguwimal milbiji dingkar-dingkaranda . Yala-yala ngayu ngayku wawu yungal ngaykuwunbu workingmananda , jalbu-jalbundu , dingkar-dingkaranda . Kaki bama ngaykundu mambarriji , and babaji ngayu buyun-buyun kidanka janandamun wawumun , ngayu jananin juran-bungal baja . ’ ” Yinya kuku Godungku Joelanda balkan , Israel-warranda balkanka .
